-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Ultimately, would you accept Tower=E2=80=99s re=
ports however they are presented? If you are suspicious of any result which i=
s not a full rebuild, we should press on with engagement of your own experts=
 at this point instead of waiting to be strung along by Tower in its process=
. As we discussed last week, to properly assess/challenge what Tower is prop=
osing, we would need independent evidence. We think that Prendos would be a g=
ood choice to undertake/review the scope. You will need to meet their cost i=
nitially,. But if they succeed in significantly changing Tower=E2=80=99s ass=
essment, their fees would be recoverable from Tower.</span><o:p></o:p></div>=
